## 11. Single Source of Truth Principles

### 11.1. Documentation Integrity
- **Avoid** duplicating information across documents
- **Reference** existing documents instead of copying content
- **Maintain** clear ownership of each piece of information
- **Update** source documents when changes are needed

### 11.2. Validation Requirements
- **Check** for information duplication
- **Verify** all references point to authoritative sources
- **Flag** contradictions between documents
- **Alert** user to any Single Source of Truth violations

### 11.3. Compliance Checklist
- [ ] No duplicate information across documents
- [ ] All references point to authoritative sources
- [ ] No contradictions with existing documentation
- [ ] Clear ownership of each information piece
- [ ] User alerted to any violations

